      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car since day one\u2014it\u2019s in flawless condition inside and out, without a single mark on it. It still has that brand-new smell and drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019m so sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to be totally obsessed! Swing by and take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
