    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This FD3S chassis represents a rare opportunity to acquire a preserved 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary icon. The powertrain maintains factory compression specs and exhibits no 'hot start' issues, with a vacuum system that remains tight and responsive. The five-speed manual gearbox offers short, tactile throws, sending power through a pristine Torsen limited-slip differential. The suspension retains its original double-wishbone geometry with factory-spec bushings, ensuring the 50/50 weight distribution is fully realized in the corners. The exterior features impeccable factory paint with no signs of oxidation or panel misalignment, while the interior maintains its driver-centric cockpit with zero bolster wear or dashboard cracking. This is an unmolested, collector-grade example for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 46500.0,
